      "note": "long title",
      "title": "To amend sections 111.41, 111.42, and 111.99 of the Revised Code to expand the Address Confidentiality Program."
    },
    {
      "note": "long title",
      "title": "To amend sections 111.41, 111.42, 111.99, 149.43, 3503.13, and 3503.24 and to enact section 3513.053 of the Revised Code to expand the Address Confidentiality Program, to exempt judges' and prosecutors' addresses from disclosure, and to make related changes to the Election Law."
